    AddressHandler
    An AddressHandler can execute an XDI operation against an address.
    Extension 
    Prototype
    This interface is used to mark messaging containers, interceptors and contributors that can create an automatically configured copy of themselves, which is useful for messaging container factories.
    Prototype.PrototypingContext 
    StatementHandler
    A StatementHandler can execute an XDI operation against a statement given in a cross-reference.
